                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1933-18350921 t18350921-1933-punishment-8"></join>DEATH</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 16.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Recommende to mercy by the Prosecutrix on account of his youth.</hi>
